task.summary: Reworking my files for the project
Uploading files for Club: Club Class, ClubRepo Interface, and ClubJDBCRepo implementation.
Created new Class DatabaseConnection to pass database Connection. Added implementation to ClubJDBCRepo as an example of how to use DatabaseConnection
Added functionality for most of ClubJDBCRepo. Can be used as an example for how the process will work. Modified UsersRepo to reflect changes
ClubJDBCRepo now talks to Controller and correctly displays data for ALL clubs. You can access this by running APIMain and going to localhost:4567/Clubs
Updated files to use PreparedStmts to stop SQL Injections. Also implemented methods in ClubJDBCRepo. All are functional except deleteClub and createClub
Added use of PLU's MySQL Database and patched Statement operations in ClubJDBCRepo
Finished implementation for Clubs entity as well as adding new class REFERENCES for Strings that contain important information.

Started implementation of Events Entity for JDBC Repo. Also created the Interface for EventRepo and the Test class for EventJDBCRepo. As of current, only the "get" commands are fully functional and implemented. Other routes will return a "Not Yet Implemented" sign.
